    <h2>Why this blog</h2>

    <p>
      I started writing here because I wanted a place to think in public. The AI space
      moves fast, and most takes are either too shallow ("AI will do everything") or
      too dismissive ("it's just autocomplete"). I'm trying to write the kind of thing
      I'd want to read — honest, specific, based on what I've actually built and used.
    </p>

    <p>
