      <li><strong>Claude &amp; LLMs in practice</strong> — what works, what doesn't, how to think about prompting and agents</li>
      <li><strong>Coding with AI</strong> — the real workflow, not the demo</li>
      <li><strong>Software engineering</strong> — how the discipline is changing, how it's staying the same</li>
      <li><strong>Misc thoughts</strong> — occasional ideas that don't fit anywhere else</li>
    </ul>

